OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDonald Wood jailed for     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsending threatening letters
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fto MPs                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man who sent threatening letters to  
OL,6, three Labour MPs before fleeing to     
OL,7, Morocco has been jailed for 21 months. 
OL,9,FDonald Wood, 84, of Barnsley, sent     
OL,10,Fthree handwritten, anonymous letters to
OL,11,Fthe offices of Dan Jarvis, John Healey 
OL,12,Fand Stephanie Peacock in March 2019.   
OL,14,FOne of the letters to Mr Jarvis, who is
OL,15,FWood's MP, referenced the death of MP  
OL,16,FJo Cox and was "particularly chilling",
OL,17,FSheffield Crown Court heard.           
OL,19,FJudge Jeremy Richardson QC said only an
OL,20,Fimmediate jail sentence was justified. 
